title: Automatic Foam Hand Soap Dispenser
overview: A smart, touchless soap dispenser with wall-mounted design, 380ml capacity, and battery level display. Ideal for bathrooms, kitchens, hotels, and restaurants to ensure hygiene and convenience.
description:
Upgrade your hygiene routine with the Automatic Foam Hand Soap Dispenser, designed for both home and commercial use. Featuring a smart sensor for touch-free operation, this dispenser ensures a clean, convenient, and safe way to wash hands without cross-contamination. With a 380ml (12.8oz) large-capacity tank, it minimizes refills while providing consistent foam dispensing.

The USB rechargeable design with a clear battery level display keeps you worry-free about power, making it both eco-friendly and cost-effective. Its wall-mounted build saves space and suits any setting, from bathrooms and kitchens to hotels, offices, and restaurants. Compatible with liquid soap, foaming soap, or shampoo, this dispenser is a versatile choice for maintaining hygiene in any environment.
